claim: History of art includes architecture, dance, sculpture, music, painting, poetry literature, theatre, narrative, film, photography and graphic arts.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The subsequent expansion of the list of principal arts in the 20th century reached to nine : architecture , dance , sculpture , music , painting , poetry  (  described broadly as a form of literature with aesthetic purpose or function , which also includes the distinct genres of theatre and narrative  )  , film , photography and graphic arts .
